creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
This is a direct connect with Grace Community Fellowship. This will keep you connected with the latest sermons from Pastor Troy Green Sr. As he teaches and preaches through God's Word. You will be kept up to date with the missions and ministries of the church and the way God is working in the body.
•There will be weekly reminders of family Bible Studies
•Reminders of weekly services
•Push Notifications of upcoming services as well as a verse for the day
•There will missions ministry updates and opportunities
•You'll hear testimonies of how Christ has changed lives

We recommend that for continual listening you connect to wifi or have an unlimited data plan due to data usage.

The Grace Community Fellowship App was created with the Subsplash App Platform.
descriptionShort: This is a direct connect with Grace Community Fellowship.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- Direct messaging is here! Admins can enable it in the Subsplash Dashboard.
- Block other users from sending you unwanted messages.
- Share prayer requests with your group channels.
- Create polls
- Reply to past messages
- Group channels can now have up to 2,000 people.

- Fixed issue causing the channel artwork to not update.
